      <title>用Hexo搭建博客的终极傻瓜式教程</title>
      <link href="2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>简介：让你复制粘贴中懒人（伪）式搭建博客（不会复制粘贴的建议<a href="https://cn.bing.com/search?q=%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E5%82%BB%E9%80%BC&qs=n&form=QBRE&sp=-1&pq=%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E5%82%BB%E9%80%BC&sc=8-4&sk=&cvid=C4D637491C4F4790B5177572D1A34B74">点这里</a>)</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="重要提示"><a href="#重要提示" class="headerlink" title="重要提示"></a>重要提示</h1><p><strong>本教程针对联想电脑，要是是别的电脑，建议去 <a href="https://www.wootec.top/2019/08/18/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8GitHub%E5%92%8CHEXO%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/">这里</a>，当然也可以选择将bat代码中的路径(比如LENOVO改成adminstrator)根据你的电脑稍作修改</strong></p><h1 id="如何用hexo搭-博-客"><a href="#如何用hexo搭-博-客" class="headerlink" title="如何用hexo搭~ 博~ 客~"></a>如何用hexo搭~ 博~ 客~</h1><blockquote><p>什么？你不知道什么是hexo？</p><blockquote><p>什么？你不知道搭博客是什么？</p></blockquote></blockquote><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E6%BB%91%E7%A8%BD1.jpg" alt="原地去世.jpg"><br>建议点击<a href="https://www.bing.com/">这里</a></p><h2 id="step1：下载两个实用软件"><a href="#step1：下载两个实用软件" class="headerlink" title="step1：下载两个实用软件"></a>step1：下载两个实用软件</h2><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/gitbash.png" alt="就是这个鬼东西"><br><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/nodejs.png" alt="和这个鬼东西"></p><blockquote><p>什么？你懒得百度？</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E7%94%9F%E6%B0%94.jpg" alt="az"></p><p><strong>彳亍口巴</strong><br><strong>你厉害</strong><br><strong><del>谁让我要写懒人教程呢</del></strong><br>把下面的代码ctrl+c,ctrl+v，也即是复制粘贴（<br>粘贴到任意一个新建的txt文件中，再将后缀名txt改为bat，双击</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang="bat" data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">title</span> 傻瓜式安装</span><br><span class="line">bitsadmin /transfer &quot;gitbash&quot; /download /priority normal &quot;https://git-scm.com/&quot; &quot;C:\Users\LENOVO\Desktop\gitbash.exe&quot; </span><br><span class="line">bitsadmin /transfer &quot;nodejs&quot; /download /priority normal  &quot;http://nodejs.cn/download/&quot; &quot;C:\Users\LENOVO\Desktop\nodejs.msi&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> C:\Users\LENOVO\Desktop\gitbash.exe</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> &quot;正在安装gitbash&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> C:\Users\LENOVO\Desktop\nodejs.msi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> &quot;正在安装nodejs&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor="red">Warning:请在下载完成后，在之前弹出的窗口按任意键继续安装，在安装完成前请勿关闭那个窗口，请务必在下载完成后再按任意键继续</td></tr></table><p>剩下的安装操作: <img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/rx1.png"><br>好！装完了！（很有精神.png）<br>(截图自伟大的Reviewer的博客（\手动滑稽）)</p><h2 id="step2：GitHub账号配置"><a href="#step2：GitHub账号配置" class="headerlink" title="step2：GitHub账号配置"></a>step2：GitHub账号配置</h2><blockquote><p>什么？你不知道GitHub？</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/az.png"></p><blockquote><p>别给我看你那白嫖的小眼神</p></blockquote><p>哈~ 哈~ 哈~<br><strong>因为这一步没得一键配置！</strong><br>所以老老实实open <a href="https://www.github.com/">https://www.github.com</a><br>老老实实注册</p><blockquote><p>不懂英语？</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/Google.png"><br><a href="https://translate.google.cn/">请</a></p><p>ps:其实微软的edge浏览器是自带翻译的（<br>注册完了以后。。。</p><h4 id="新建仓库"><a href="#新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="新建仓库"></a>新建仓库</h4><p>取什么名字？</p><blockquote><p>你的用户名.github.io</p><p><em>提前祝贺不看后面就随便起了一个奇奇怪怪名字的同学，以后你的博客网址就是这个（买了域名的阔佬除外)</em></p></blockquote><h2 id="step3-配置git"><a href="#step3-配置git" class="headerlink" title="step3:配置git"></a>step3:配置git</h2><p><strong>如果你看到这里，接下来别抱怨作者的排版（指到处都是的文章内链接），难道你没看到这篇文章的分类么？🤪</strong><br><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/huaji.jpg"><br>双击桌面上的Gitbash图标，然后<br><strong>1.新建文件夹作为博客文件夹(名字？<a href="#t">点这里</a>)<br>2.进入该文件夹，右键，git bash here。<br>3.配置账户</strong><br>把下面的代码复制粘贴到任意一个新建的txt文件中，<br>再将后缀名txt改为bat，双击</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang="bat" data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> /p a=put your github username: </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> /p b=put your github register e-mail: </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;gitname&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;git config --global user.name <span class="variable">%a%</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;gitmail&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;git config --global user.email <span class="variable">%b%</span>&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>4.配置SSH key</strong><br>复制下面的代码，输入到gitbash页面</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>什么？你失败了？<br><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/openssh.png"><br>–摘自伟大的Reviewer的博客</p><p>建议出门<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38328382/article/details/103731377">左转</a>😶</p><p><small><small><small><em>这种东西一般不都是默认开启的么（当然要是win7，当我没说）</em></small></small></small><br>然后回车回车回车回车…</p><p><strong>5.部署SSH key</strong><br>打开<a href="https://github.com/settings/keys">Github_Settings_keys</a>,新建new SSH Key<br><small><small><small><del>懒得放图片了</del></small></small></small><br>然后从C:\Users\LENOVO里的.ssh找到id_rsa.pub（盲猜直接打不开），改为txt后缀（你要是直接打开了。。。e，你厉害）<br>复制里面的内容，粘贴到新建的key里面<br>标题？这种东西数据对了就行</p><p><span id="t">标题你就是取个I am god都没人管你 😂 </span><br>然后复制下面的命令到gitbash里</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果出现Hi,XXXX!You’ve successfully……..之类的，那么你就成功了</p><h2 id="step4-Hexo本地博客搭建"><a href="#step4-Hexo本地博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="step4:Hexo本地博客搭建"></a>step4:Hexo本地博客搭建</h2><blockquote><p>下面开始一键操作！</p></blockquote><p>同样把下面的代码复制粘贴到任意一个新建的txt文件中，<br>再将后缀名txt改为bat，双击</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang="bat" data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> /p a=put your file name:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;download hexo&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;npm install -g hexo-cli&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;hexo push&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;hexo init <span class="variable">%a%</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;hexo view&quot; &quot;hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>我们不生产代码，我们只是代码的搬运工🤪</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/OIP.jpg"></p><p>(传说中某些前端工程师的键盘😒)</p><p><span id="b"> </span></p><table><tr><td bgcolor="red">Warning:请在gitbash窗口关闭后，在之前弹出的cmd窗口按任意键继续安装，在安装完成前请勿关闭cmd窗口，请务必在gitbash窗口关闭后再按任意键继续</td></tr></table><p>ps:1.安装过程，即第一个git窗口执行时，会很慢…<br>   2.初始化过程同样慢炸…</p><blockquote><p>因为……我们有伟大的万里长城防火墙啊…… ( 逃</p></blockquote><p> –Reviewer如是说。<br>总结hexo用法：</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo -g #安装Hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm update hexo -g #升级</span><br><span class="line">hexo init #初始化博客</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>点击<a href="http://localhost:4000/">这里</a>可以预览你的本地博客</p><h2 id="step5-将本地博客发布到GitHub页面上"><a href="#step5-将本地博客发布到GitHub页面上" class="headerlink" title="step5:将本地博客发布到GitHub页面上"></a>step5:将本地博客发布到GitHub页面上</h2><hr><p><strong>看到效果图，你以为博客就这样建完了？</strong><br>事实上，当你访问 <span id="k"><a href="https://yourgithubname.github.io/">https://yourgithubname.github.io</a></span> (yourgithubname指你的GitHub账号名)时，你会发现<br><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/404.png"><br><strong>Surprise!<del>Congratulations!</del></strong></p><hr><p>先在你的博客文件夹打开_config.yml文件</p><blockquote><p>如果你是第一次打开，八成会问你打开方式…</p><p>这个时候选择记事本…</p></blockquote><p>拉到最下面，你会看到：</p><p class="code-caption" data-lang="yml" data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>下面是复制粘贴时间！</p><p>老样子，复制粘贴，建bat文件</p></blockquote><p class="code-caption" data-lang="bat" data-line_number="frontend" data-trim_indent="backend" data-label_position="outer" data-labels_left="Code" data-labels_right=":" data-labels_copy="Copy code"><span class="code-caption-label"></span><a class="code-caption-copy">Copy code</a></p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;download hexo&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;npm install hexo-deploy-git --save&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;download hexo&quot; &quot;C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot; -c &quot;hexo clean&amp;&amp;hexo g -d&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pause</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>warning:懒得写了，<a href="#b">上去</a>看吧（<br>wait…………….<br><strong>等窗口关闭，通过<a href="#k">这个</a>访问你自己的博客！</strong></p><hr><p>你会惊奇的发现：</p><ul><li><input checked disabled type="checkbox"> 你的博客搭建完成</li></ul><hr><h2 id="step6-写博文"><a href="#step6-写博文" class="headerlink" title="step6:写博文"></a>step6:写博文</h2><p><strong><em>不肝了，再肝人要猝死</em></strong><br><img src="/2020/11/13/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%81%E5%82%BB%E7%93%9C%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/ge.jpg"></p>]]></content>
      
      
